dical, veterinary, telephones, door-to-door delivery, Banks, Private Security companies, cleaning services, garbage collection, fire-brigade, petrol stations, water departments, and some KCCA staff should continue to operate. URA ordered not to close business on account of not paying taxes in these 14 days. 20. Gatherings of more than 5 persons are hereby prohibited. 21. Permission can be sought from the government authorities to use private transport to take such persons to the hospital.  googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('div-gpt-ad-1584621281588-0'); }); Are you suspecting that you have coronavirus? Before you rush to the hospital, do this quick easy self-assessment test. #StayHome #WashYourHands HERE. Are you suspecting that you have coronavirus? Before you rush to the hospital, do this quick easy self-assessment test. #StayHome #WashYourHands HERE. Before you rush to the hospital, do this quick easy self-assessment test. #StayHome #WashYourHands HERE.  #mc_embed_signup{background:#fff; clear:left; font:14px Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; }
